  dsimp only [SemiconjBy]
  <;>
  simp_all [MulOpposite.mul, unop]
  <;>
  congr 1 <;>
  simp_all [mul_assoc, mul_comm, mul_left_comm]
  <;>
  aesop
```

This completes the proof by showing the equivalence between the two statements about semiconjugacy in `α` and `αᵐᵒᵖ`.
